<pardef id='3' align='center' spaceafter='2' keepwithnext='true' keeptogether='true'/>
<par def='3'><run><font size='12pt' name='Microsoft JhengHei' pitch='variable'
 truetype='true' familyid='20' color='#bfdbfe'/>Dormitory Management Information System</run></par></tablecell></tablerow>
<tablerow>
<tablecell bgcolor='#eff6ff'>
<pardef id='4' align='center' spacebefore='2' spaceafter='2'/>
<par def='4'><run><font size='11pt' name='Microsoft JhengHei' pitch='variable'
 truetype='true' familyid='20' color='#334155'/>整合 房間、申請、訪客、違規 四大模組的一站式宿舍管理平台。請點選上方按鈕進入各功能模組。</run></par></tablecell></tablerow></table>
